						               													<description>This fun and exciting trivia-style board game will put your knowledge to the test and provide hours of entertainment for the whole family. Reveal is a dynamic and engaging board game with a difference: there are no questions, only answers!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Reveal can be played as individuals or in teams and the object of the game is to guess the hidden movie, TV show and song titles to gain medals and walk the red carpet to be crowned Champion of the Titles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The answer card is loaded into the Reveal card sleeve and then the card is pulled out to reveal only the first letter of each of the words in the title. The player then has two guesses, or 30 seconds, to correctly name the title and win three medals. An incorrect guess will result in the second letter of each of the title words being revealed but the quicker the title is guessed the more medals that are won! Once a player has scooped 15 medals it is time to head for the winner&amp;rsquo;s square at the centre of the board via any of the Red Carpet routes. In order to be crowned the ultimate Champion of the Titles a player must solve one final title from a category chosen by an opponent!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
